      &copy; {currentYear} Holger Grosse-Plankermann. All rights reserved.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-4 text-sm md:text-sm text-secondary items-center">
      <div class="flex gap-3 md:gap-4">
        <a href="/impressum" class="text-accent hover:underline">Imprint/Impressum</a>
        <a href="/datenschutz" class="text-accent hover:underline">Privacy/Datenschutz</a>
